# Simulation output is stored separately (see README) — the 3D field and slice
# files run to hundreds of MB each and exceed GitHub's 100 MB per-file limit.
*.jld2
*.nc

# Julia checkpoints
**/*_checkpoint_iteration*.jld2

# ...but keep the horizontally-averaged profile statistics. These are small
# (~25 MB each) and are the data every figure is computed from, so they are
# worth version-controlling alongside the analysis scripts.
!*_profiles.jld2
